name: Soyuz 1
notes: Crew died when parachutes did not open

name: Apollo 9
notes: First rendezvous and docking with a Lunar lander

name: Apollo 13
notes: Following explosion on second day of mission, critically damaging the service module, Lunar landing aborted. Miraculously, all astronauts returned safely to Earth

name: Soyuz 11
notes: First space station rendezvous and docking; crew perished from asphyxiation, only people to die in space

name: Apollo 15
notes: First use of a lunar roving vehicle (LRV)

name: Skylab 2
notes: First American space station rendezvouz and docking
